The paper discusses reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on learning a task and transferring skills suggests that the paper may also fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The use of an agent in an environment suggests that robotics (cs.RO) may also be a relevant sub-category. The mention of developing a sense of survival suggests that the paper may also fall under the category of control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the evaluation of the approach in an environment suggests that computer vision (cs.CV) may also be a relevant sub-category.
